<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>보고서 작성</title>
  <link href="/css/report.css?v=1.0" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

</head>

<body>
  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header class="header__container">
    <!-- Site H1 / display: none -->
    <h1 class="main-title">노긋노긋메인홈</h1>
    <div class="header__block">
      <a href="/Detail"> 마이페이지 </a>
      <a href="/logout"> 로그아웃 </a>
    </div>
    <div class="header_nav-main-block">
      <!-- 네비게이션에 해당하는 부분 -->
      <nav class="header__nav-block">
        <ul class="nav__list" role="navigation">
          <li class="nav__list-item">
            <a href="/main" aria-label="노긋노긋 홈페이지">
              <img src="/images/logo.png" width="50" alt="로고">
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__list-item">
            <a href="/filter"> 매칭 </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__list-item">
            <a href="/chat"> 채팅 </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__list-item">
            <a href="/promiseList"> 약속 </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__list-item">
            <a href="/postList/1"> 게시판 </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="side__nav-container">
      <ul class="nav__list" role="navigation">
        <li class="nav__review__list-item">
          <a href="/reportList">보고서 목록</a>
        <li class="nav__review__list-item"><a href="/reportexample"> 예시 </a></li>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="report__container" id="container">
      <h1 class="title">활동 보고서 작성</h1>
      <div class="notice__container">
        <span class="notice">보고서는 활동 후 3일 이내에 작성해야 합니다.</span>
        <span class="notice">활동 내용은 진행한 수업에 대한 간단한 내용을 포함해야 합니다.</span>
        <span class="notice">자세하게 작성할 필요는 없으나 당일 수업에서 무엇을 했는지 알 수 있을 정도로 작성합니다.</span>
        <span class="notice__red">한 번 작성한 보고서는 수정이 불가능하니 신중하게 작성해주세요.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="report__write" id="container1">
        <form id="reportForm" action="/submitReport" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <input type="hidden" name="promiseNum" value="<%= promiseDetails.promiseNum %>">
          <input type="hidden" name="seniorNum" value="<%= promiseDetails.seniorNum %>">
          <input type="hidden" name="stdNum" value="<%= promiseDetails.studentNum %>">
          <div id="contents" class="content">
            <h3 for="reportContent" class="content__title">활동 내용</h3>
            <textarea class="reportContent" id="reportContent" name="reportContent" rows="4" cols="50"
              required></textarea><br>
          </div>
          <div class="picture">
            <h3 id="text" class="content__title">사진</h3>
            <div class="image__container">
              <input type="file" id="fileInput" name="reportMedia" accept="image/*" style="display: none;"
                onchange="previewImage(event)" required>
              <div id="reportMedia" onclick="openFileUploader()">
                <img id="plusButton" src="/images/plus.png"
                  style="width: 30px; height: 30px; margin-top: 130px; cursor: pointer;">
              </div>
              <img id="uploadImagePreview"
                style="width: 90px; height: 90px; display: none; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="button">
            <button type="submit">확인</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <footer class="footer__container">
    <section class="pages__container">
      <a href="#">이용약관</a>
      <a href="#">개인정보처리방침</a>
      <a href="#">커뮤니티이용규칙</a>
      <a href="#">문의하기</a>
    </section>
  </footer>
</body>
<script>
  function openFileUploader() {
    document.getElementById('fileInput').click();
  }
  function previewImage(event) {
    document.getElementById('plusButton').style.display = "none";
    var input = event.target;
    var reader = new FileReader();
    reader.onload = function () {
      var dataURL = reader.result;
      var output = document.getElementById('uploadImagePreview');
      output.src = dataURL;
      output.style.display = "block";
      output.style.width = "200px";
      output.style.height = "200px";
    };
    reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
  } 
</script>

</html>